## Response

Get participant profile by number.
```
{
    "data": {
        "participant": {
            "pid": "2lrkzingy4WFmkluDjpwMqSdfdz1",
            "pid_alias": "2015",
            "participant_name_first": "George",
            "participant_name_last": "Saenz",
            "status": "Active Engaged",
            "participant_name_preferred": "George",
            "__typename": "TypeParticipant"
        }
    }
}
```

body.text:
{"query":"query ParticipantByNumber($phone: String!) {
  participant: participantByNumber(phone: $phone) {
    pid
    pid_alias
    participant_name_first
    participant_name_last
    status
    participant_name_preferred
    __typename
  }
}","variables":{"phone":"916-636-2888"},"operationName":"ParticipantByNumber"}
